### ====================================================
### CODELAB 02 — Pruebas de Actuator y Datos de Prueba
### ====================================================
### Cada request es independiente y ejecutable por separado
### Usa el puerto local 8082 cuando ejecutes con Spring Boot
### Usa el puerto Docker 8085 cuando ejecutes con Docker Compose

###

### ====================================================
### PARTE 1: VERIFICAR DATOS CARGADOS EN LA BASE DE DATOS
### ====================================================

### 1. Verificar que hay componentes cargados (Local)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/components
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Verificar que hay componentes cargados (Docker)
GET http://localhost:8085/api/v1/component-service/components
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Verificar que hay CPUs cargados (Local)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/cpus
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Verificar que hay CPUs cargados (Docker)
GET http://localhost:8085/api/v1/component-service/cpus
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Verificar que hay GPUs cargadas (Local)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/gpus
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Verificar que hay GPUs cargadas (Docker)
GET http://localhost:8085/api/v1/component-service/gpus
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Verificar que hay RAMs cargadas (Local)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/rams
Accept: application/json

###

### 8. Verificar que hay RAMs cargadas (Docker)
GET http://localhost:8085/api/v1/component-service/rams
Accept: application/json

###

### 9. Verificar que hay Motherboards cargadas (Local)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/motherboards
Accept: application/json

###

### 10. Verificar que hay Motherboards cargadas (Docker)
GET http://localhost:8085/api/v1/component-service/motherboards
Accept: application/json

###

### 11. Verificar que hay PSUs cargadas (Local)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/psus
Accept: application/json

###

### 12. Verificar que hay PSUs cargadas (Docker)
GET http://localhost:8085/api/v1/component-service/psus
Accept: application/json

###

### ====================================================
### PARTE 2: HEALTH CHECK Y MÉTRICAS DE ACTUATOR (Local)
### ====================================================

### 13. Health check — debe mostrar status UP (Local)
GET http://localhost:8082/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

###

### 14. Health check — debe mostrar status UP (Docker)
GET http://localhost:8085/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

###

### 15. Información de la aplicación (Local)
GET http://localhost:8082/actuator/info
Accept: application/json

###

### 16. Lista de todas las métricas disponibles (Local)
GET http://localhost:8082/actuator/metrics
Accept: application/json

###

### 17. Memoria JVM usada (Local)
GET http://localhost:8082/actuator/metrics/jvm.memory.used
Accept: application/json

###

### 18. Conexiones activas de HikariCP (Local)
GET http://localhost:8082/actuator/metrics/hikaricp.connections.active
Accept: application/json

###

### 19. Conexiones inactivas de HikariCP (Local)
GET http://localhost:8082/actuator/metrics/hikaricp.connections.idle
Accept: application/json

###

### 20. Todos los endpoints REST registrados (Local)
GET http://localhost:8082/actuator/mappings
Accept: application/json

###

### 21. Todos los endpoints REST registrados (Docker)
GET http://localhost:8085/actuator/mappings
Accept: application/json

###

### ====================================================
### PARTE 3: CREAR COMPONENTES NUEVOS (Local)
### ====================================================

### 22. Crear un CPU nuevo (Local)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/cpus
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brand": "AMD",
  "model": "Ryzen 9 7950X",
  "price": 3399000,
  "socket": "AM5",
  "cores": 16,
  "threads": 32,
  "tdp": 170
}

###

### 23. Crear una GPU nueva (Local)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/gpus
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brand": "NVIDIA",
  "model": "RTX 4080 SUPER",
  "price": 5499000,
  "vram": 16,
  "tdp": 320,
  "pcieVersion": "PCIe 4.0"
}

###

### 24. Crear una RAM nueva (Local)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/rams
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brand": "Corsair",
  "model": "Vengeance RGB",
  "price": 459900,
  "type": "DDR5",
  "capacity": 32,
  "speed": 6000
}

###

### 25. Crear una Motherboard nueva (Local)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/motherboards
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brand": "ASUS",
  "model": "ROG Strix X670E-E",
  "price": 1899000,
  "socket": "AM5",
  "ramType": "DDR5",
  "maxRam": 192,
  "pcieVersion": "PCIe 5.0"
}

###

### 26. Crear una PSU nueva (Local)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/psus
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brand": "Seasonic",
  "model": "Focus GX-850",
  "price": 899900,
  "wattage": 850,
  "efficiency": "80+ Gold"
}

###

